Package: CircadianTools
Type: Package
Title: Collection of Tools for Detecting Rhythmic Genes 
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2019-07-05
Authors@R: person("Nathan","Constantine-Cooke", email="nsc@aber.ac.uk", role=c("cre","aut"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <nsc@aber.ac.uk>
Description: Allows Cosinor Models and Turning Point Analysis to be easily carried out on transcriptomics data using R. Designed to be as flexible as possible such as by allowing an unequal number of replicates.
URL: https://github.com/nathansam/CircadianTools
